project_descr: The Project “Establishment and Development of Business Incubators in Romania” aims to support the entrepreneurial spirit and economic development of the targeted areas, by through the development of the SME sector.

outputs.output_descr: Establishment of a network of business incubators that would foster sustainable livelihoods in Romania through SME development and building of national and local capacity.

project_title: establishment and dev. of business incubators
